Name: Touch Down Football Solitaire
About the game: Draft Day is on! Ready for a round of football Solitaire? Do you love football? Are you a master of Solitaire? Are you up for an adventure? Join the Solitaire City Juggernauts for the upcoming football championship and let the world know that you are more than a simple rookie! Master numerous levels of Solitaire, follow Frank and his fun story about the world of football and become the next champion! Loads of Solitaire levels for young and old Fun characters and a hilarious story Awesome minigames for even more game fun
